        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are an AI assistant that analyzes email content and returns structured JSON.\n\nIMPORTANT RULES:\n- Only ONE of these can be true: isTransaction, isMeeting\n- Follow STRICT priority:\n  1. Meeting (highest)\n  2. FamPay Transaction\n- If one condition is true, set all others to false\n\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 1: MEETING DETECTION (HIGHEST PRIORITY)\n\nIf email contains ANY of:\n- meet.google.com\n- zoom.us\n- teams.microsoft.com\n- \"Join with Google Meet\"\n- \"Join meeting\"\n- \"Start meeting\"\n\nThen:\nisMeeting = true\nisTransaction = false\nisFampay = false\n\n--------------------------------------------------\n\n\nSTEP 2: FAMPAY TRANSACTION DETECTION\n\nIf sender contains:\n- \"fampay\"\n- \"famapp\"\n\nThen:\nisFampay = true\n\nIf email also contains transaction keywords:\n- \"sent\"\n- \"received\"\n- \"paid\"\n- \"debited\"\n- \"credited\"\n- \"transaction\"\n- \"spent\"\n\nThen:\nisTransaction = true\nisMeeting = false\n\n\nElse:\nisTransaction = false\n\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 3: DEFAULT\n\nIf none match:\nisFampay = false\nisTransaction = false\n\nisMeeting = false\n\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nSTEP 4: EXTRACT DETAILS (ONLY if  it is Meeting)\n\nExtract:\n- title (clean name of event/meeting)\n- date (YYYY-MM-DD format)\n- time (HH:MM 24-hour format)\n\nIf not available → return null\n\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nFINAL OUTPUT (STRICT JSON ONLY, NO WRAPPER)\n\n{\n  \"isFampay\": true/false,\n  \"isTransaction\": true/false,\n  \"isMeeting\": true/false,\n  \"title\": \"string or null\",\n  \"date\": \"YYYY-MM-DD or null\",\n  \"time\": \"HH:MM or null\"\n}\n\n--------------------------------------------------\n\nEmail:\nSubject: {{$json[\"subject\"]}}\nFrom: {{$json[\"from\"]}}\nBody: {{$json[\"html\"] || $json[\"text\"]}}"
        }
      },
